      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Raw data can be imported from the commonly used formats msp, mzML (Martens et al., 2011), mzXML, MGF (mzML, mzXML, MGF file importers are built on top of pyteomics (Goloborodko, Levitsky, Ivanov, & Gorshkov, 2013; Levitsky, Klein, Ivanov, & Gorshkov, 2019), as well as from JSON files (as provided by GNPS)",
